# Exception: each format's permanently pinned b-roll clip is a small,
# deliberately committed static asset (not rendered/generated output) --
# one fixed real clip per format (ambience/short/live), chosen by the
# channel owner from real Pixabay downloads; the illustrated *_clip.mp4
# variants stay committed too as the last-resort fallback if a real clip
# ever goes missing. Only the audio bed varies run to run.
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_clip.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_clip.json
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_short_clip.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_short_clip.json
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_ambience.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_ambience.json
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_live.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_live.json
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_short_real.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_storm_short_real.json
!_assets/video/pinned_classical_ambience.mp4
!_assets/video/pinned_classical_ambience.json

